    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无尽的阴云阻挡了一切信号, 连噪音也一日日消失不见, 沉默充斥着无线电平原的每个角落。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直到有一天, 一阵来自接收器的嘈杂的声音打破了死寂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这一天,一个期待信号的收音机——小否踏上了旅程。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一个难度较低的平台跳跃游戏,有少量战斗要素。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以控制一个小收音机在游戏世界中探索,当玩家拿到第一个能力时,会发现角色化作了人形。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但如果不小心受伤,则会变回收音机形态……所以最好不要受伤哦! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基本挑战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在精心设计的关卡中,躲避环境中的陷阱,发射&quot;播放按钮&quot;触发机关、攻击敌人。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基本挑战较为简单。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119380/extras/0eb0bf916b5523f32ed741b818a31185.poster.avif?t=1750168828\" width=450 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119380/extras/0eb0bf916b5523f32ed741b818a31185.webm?t=1750168828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119380/extras/0eb0bf916b5523f32ed741b818a31185.mp4?t=1750168828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >进阶挑战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关卡中存在一些宝石,将其带到对应颜色的宝石孔位,就可以完成挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宝石挑战有的难有的简单,不强制限制玩家</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119380/extras/d38df0dad490b6cab19280a38fde888b.poster.avif?t=1750168828\" width=474 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119380/extras/d38df0dad490b6cab19280a38fde888b.webm?t=1750168828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119380/extras/d38df0dad490b6cab19280a38fde888b.mp4?t=1750168828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >隐藏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关卡中存在着一些隐藏,等着你的发现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119380/extras/29e1883764aacea8e6ee40c20351aa14.poster.avif?t=1750168828\" width=474 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119380/extras/29e1883764aacea8e6ee40c20351aa14.webm?t=1750168828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119380/extras/29e1883764aacea8e6ee40c20351aa14.mp4?t=1750168828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Boss战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >到达关底,你需要和一个巨大的音响战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗有两个阶段。最终阶段有一定难度,每三次激光中,会有一次的激光非常难缠。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果想要无伤通过,玩家需要开动脑筋才能找到应对此招式的最优走位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119380/extras/c056664807a30565e44ea99a17de0d92.poster.avif?t=1750168828\" width=474 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119380/extras/c056664807a30565e44ea99a17de0d92.webm?t=1750168828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119380/extras/c056664807a30565e44ea99a17de0d92.mp4?t=1750168828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >插画收集</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏有两张插画,每张插画有一个差分,一共四个项目,可以通过完成下面这些目标来解锁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成大部分宝石挑战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成全部宝石挑战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成功击败Boss</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无伤击败Boss</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119380/extras/1021771bd9e99aa000fe9b32965c34c1.avif?t=1750168828\" width=600 height=310 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >声明</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏使用的所有美术素材(除了部分由开发者自己手动绘制的)均为本人委托优秀的画师们亲手绘制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前我还是个新人制作人,没有足够数量的玩家朋友可以交流,希望喜爱萌系/可爱游戏的朋友可以加群讨论,还请多多指教。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏制作：期喵 <br>游戏发行：宇宙列车 <br>玩家交流群：1002444165</p>",
